text: Late-shift glow on a pastel street, Spin-up hum as the model heats. Prompt on a napkin, you smile, “Let’s try,” Latté foam renders a clouded sky. Cassette-heart click, buffer lights blink, Your laugh uploads and I’m on the brink— Cursor of neon tracing your face, We hit “go live” on a brand-new place. Sticker-frame UI round neon signs, Parallax lanes like data lines; We sync our steps to a MIDI clock, Low-latency love with a velvet lock.
